data.description: Welcome Home to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom located in Liberty County.This home contains 2,278 square feet of living space with a 2 car garage. This home has formal dining area with stylish columns a spacious family room with an electric fireplace. The kitchen has plenty of counter space with a designated pantry and kitchen island. The master bedroom has a spacious attached en-suite to enjoy. The master bedroom has separate vanities, garden tub , separate shower and a walk in closet. Don't miss your opportunity to view and own this home.
